# OpenAPI Annotation Demo

[route, serve, Response, Request](std/http.ssc)
[openapi](std/openapi.ssc)

```scalascript
@openapi(
  summary = "Get user",
  description = "Returns a single user by id.",
  tags = List("users")
)
route("GET", "/users/:id") { req =>
  Response.json(Map("id" -> req.params("id")))
}

serve(8080)
```
